onspiracy that threatens to consume every living soul upon the islands. They must unravel the secrets of the isles and face the shadows that lurk in the mists if they are to defeat the <strong>Bloodlords of the Deep</strong>.</p><p></p><h2><strong>Plug-in Adventure</strong></h2><p>This module is a 5e adventure designed for a party of five level 10 characters, built to be plugged easily into an existing campaign or as a short stand-alone adventure.</p><p></p><h2><strong>Background</strong></h2><p>Long ago, when gods walked the earth, the goddess Thess dwelled in the mortal realm, ruling over her chosen followers from her island dominion. As the time of the gods waned and the world was to be passed into mortal hands, Thess looked out upon her faithful, and refused to abandon them. Choosing to be inextricably bound to the world, she stayed behind as one by one the other gods departed, consigning herself to a slow diminishing.</p><p>Many centuries later, a visitor from the stars arrived on Thess’ isles. An ancient eldritch being known only as the Elder One crash-landed upon the isles. Weakened by its fall, it sought to devour the isles’ inhabitants to replenish its power and resume its astral journey. With her powers now almost faded entirely, Thess sacrificed her own physical form to seal the monstrosity away in a prison of gleaming coral, and entrusted the last of her power to her half-mortal descendants.</p><p>As time turned and legend passed into myth, the Elder One began to stir in its prison. Reaching out with its loathsome mind, it found a desperate soul that it could manipulate – a priestess of Thess called Sarenya, who was gradually succumbing to a wasting disease. Determined to save herself, she followed its voice down into the depths of the isles and drank the blood that oozed from its prison, becoming a horrendous, aberrant thing, neither living nor dead – a vampiric monster bound to the Elder One’s will. Using the power bestowed upon her by the Elder One, she subverted the priesthood of the isles from within, turning her favoured servants into vampiric monsters like herself, and has ruled the isles from the shadows since.</p><p>She awaits the day when Thess’ last descendants regain enough of the goddess’ power that they can be sacrificed to her dread master and restore its full strength…</p><p></p><h2><strong>Adventure Overview</strong></h2><p></p><p>Part I - The Voyage (Combat, Seafaring). The characters navigate the high seas on the way to the Isles of Thess and are ambushed by vampiric monsters.</p><p>Part II - Into the Mist (Combat, Exploration, Mystery). The characters must explore the mists of Thess in search of the Fairy Queen’s missing captain.</p><p>Part III - The Elder One (Boss Battle, Exploration). The characters must delve beneath the island to face off against Lady Sarenya and her dark master.</p><p></p><h2><strong>Credits</strong></h2><p><strong>Head of Content &amp; Editor</strong> - Nadav Brand</p><p><strong>Head Writer</strong> - Daniel Smith</p><p><strong>3D Sculptor</strong> - David Pereira</p><p><strong>Graphic Design</strong> - Callum Dare</p><p><strong>Maps</strong> - In collaboration with Elysium Cartography, GoAdventureMaps, &amp; Meditating Munky Maps</p><p><strong>Content Consultant</strong> - Rob Leonard</p><p><strong>Playtesters</strong> - Lukas Edelmann, Aarushi Menon, James Sutton, Jesse Carse, rAzimovTW, MisterChau.</p><p></p><p><strong>Thank you to all our Patreons &amp; Tribers!</strong></p><p></p><p>For more adventures visit mammothfactorygames.com</p>","markdown":""},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}}],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1665867245328,"modifiedTime":1665976468878,"lastModifiedBy":"cP1aqbcSMQN2jq1L"},"_id":"y7OppMi1yxXETRo3","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"cP1aqbcSMQN2jq1L":3}}
